items.title: Trump loses bid for appeals court bid to rehear E. Jean Carroll case
items.description: Trump was ordered to pay E. Jean Carroll $5 million in the case by a New York federal jury which found he had sexually abused and defamed the writer.

items.title: Trump urges Iran to reach nuclear deal 'before there is nothing left'
items.description: "Iran must make a deal, before there is nothing left, and save what was once known as the Iranian Empire," the Washington leader said.

items.title: Israel-Iran strikes likely just the opening salvo as region and markets brace for what comes next
items.description: Israel's overnight missile barrage was the largest attack on the Islamic Republic since the Iran-Iraq war of the 1980s.
